Druid nukes are on par with mage nukes. Very little difference.<br>
Druid damage shields are very very similar to mages. Very little difference.<br>
<br>
A druid's dire charmed pet hits for more than my best pet at level 65 fully focused with Time focus, has more hitpoints, and can easily win in a duel. I have a link that will prove this. However, the limits on direcharm being animal only and the exp penalty incurred using DC pets balances this.<br>
